ctrl.py
class that runs the controller. Calls a class controlling a single 
function such as hot water tun heating.

Each controller class should at least have defs for 

__init__: setting everything up
__del__: shutting everything down, will probably use stop
stop: Stopping all functionality safely. Shutting off all power etc.
get: Get current measured value, such as temperature
set: Setting desired target value such as temperature
done: boolean, if target is reached. This will indicate that the current stage is complete.


